case.name: Hilda! Hilda!
case.description: Hilda said her own name when she finished, and now she's trying to be casual about it

case.name: Hilda Pointy Ears
case.description: Hilda reveals Seteth's secret pointy ears, then awkwardly tries to cover for herself

case.name: Hilda's Deception Revealed (Main)
case.description: Hilda just revealed that her cluelessness at playing poker at the beginning of the game was all an act to try to make the others freely give her an advantage! May also occur elsewhere, see "Hilda's Deception Revealed" both "(Main)" and "Winner"

case.name: Hilda's Deception Revealed (Alt)
case.description: Hilda just revealed that her cluelessness at playing poker at the beginning of the game was all an act to try to make the others freely give her an advantage! May also occur elsewhere, see "Hilda's Deception Revealed" both "(Main)" and "Winner"

case.name: Hilda's Scarf Woes
case.description: Hilda resents the idea of having to re-tie the scarf she just took off.

case.name: Fishing For Compliments
case.description: Hilda actively seeks compliments on her masturbation.

case.name: Round One Reveal
case.description: Hilda is clueless about poker, and tells the other players about her cards before the reveal. The tag "RoundOneReveal" applies to all lines of this sort, but specific hands can be targeted with the unique markers that begin with "HildaReveal"

case.name: Hilda's Deception Revealed (Winner)
case.description: Having already won, Hilda just revealed that her cluelessness at playing poker at the beginning of the game was all an act to try to make the others freely give her an advantage! May also be triggered by losing layers, see "Hilda's Deception Revealed", both "(Main)" and "(Alt)".

notes.note: Yes, Hilda's second line here is very deliberately ironic.
Hilda is notably perceptive - she definitely knows there's something up with Marth by this point, but she's not going to steal Lucina's thunder by revealing her secret
This line was written before the existence of Summer Hilda
